gw.api.webservice.messagingTools
Class MessageOptionalFields

java.lang.Object
  gw.api.webservice.messagingTools.MessageOptionalFields
All Implemented Interfaces:
GWRemotable
Deprecated. replaced by plugin-based messaging. Use the MessageTransport, MessageRequest, and MessageReply plugins instead. 

public class MessageOptionalFields
extends java.lang.Object
implements GWRemotable

Container class for the optional message fields that can be set in the message template. These fields are passed to the send() method of MessageSink, and are also returned from the ack methods of AckHandler. The contents of these fields are completely up to the template designer; ClaimCenter just persists them with the message for the convenience of the integration layer.
